## Auth

-   Filament auth page: [app/Filament/Pages/Auth/Login.php](mdc:app/Filament/Pages/Auth/Login.php)
-   Password reset: [app/Http/Controllers/Auth/ForgotPasswordController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/Auth/ForgotPasswordController.php), [app/Http/Controllers/Auth/ResetPasswordController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/Auth/ResetPasswordController.php)

## Conventions

-   Keep middleware registration in [app/Http/Kernel.php](mdc:app/Http/Kernel.php)
-   Exception handling in `app/Exceptions/Handler.php` (default Laravel 10 layout)
-   Prefer Eloquent relationships and Resources for CRUD (see [app/Filament/Resources](mdc:app/Filament/Resources))
